{"tid":202894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓今早試射飛彈 據傳失敗","createTime":"2017-04-15T23:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T12:33:09.000Z","uid":35790,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c5ee80e17294b29fec0e35ee453f004b922ef1b","tid":202894,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:28:40.000Z","msg":"北韓今早試射飛彈 據傳失敗<br />\n2017-04-16 07:20聯合報 記者郭宣含╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓軍方表示，北韓今天早上在朝鮮半島東岸新浦地區試射飛彈，飛彈型號未知，據信試射失敗。<br />\n(聯合) <br />\n北朝鮮がミサイル発射に失敗 韓国軍発表<br />\n<br />\n4月16日 8時19分<br />\n<br />\n韓国軍の合同参謀本部は、北朝鮮が１６日朝、東部のハムギョン（咸鏡）南道シンポ（新浦）付近から、何らかのミサイルの発射を試みたものの、失敗したと見られると発表しました。韓国軍はアメリカ軍とともに、詳しい情報の収集を急いでいます。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20170416/k10010950171000.html?utm_int=news-new_contents_list-items_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20170416%2Fk10010950171000.html%3Futm_int%3Dnews-new_contents_list-items_001&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7Bzcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0661a1b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20170416/k10010950171000.html?utm_int=news-new_contents_list-items_001</a>"},{"pid":"8946ee111dcbb1205f75bfdba1da162c1241dba6","tid":202894,"uid":11677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65868b143c3c6f65ea1245486ab168b141278063","tid":202894,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:30:35.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963de671105ba2073cf0e3c750f5dc0e54dfe7d3","tid":202894,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:31:27.000Z","msg":"跟住搞核試"},{"pid":"caeefc6664ba3b1ac963fa7c8e7b801212293386","tid":202894,"uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:31:37.000Z","msg":"咁重炸唔炸平壤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hk